OL,3,CIranian state TV says Supreme Leader
OL,4,CAyatollah Ali Khamenei has died
OL,6,FIranian state TV said the country's
OL,7,FSupreme Leader Ayatollah Ali Khamenei
OL,8,Fhas died.
OL,10,FThe Associated Press reported state TV
OL,11,Fgave no cause for the 86-year-old's
OL,12,Fdeath, with the announcement following
OL,13,Fjoint US-Israeli strikes on the
OL,14,Fcountry.
OL,16,FIt comes after US President Donald
OL,17,FTrump claimed Khamenei had died in the
OL,18,Fattacks on Saturday morning and urged
OL,19,Fthe Iranian people to seize "the
OL,20,Fsingle greatest chance ... to take
OL,21,Fback their country".
