OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772478696
OL,3,CIranian state TV says Supreme Leader
OL,4,CAyatollah Ali Khamenei has died
OL,6,FThe Government has not yet commented
OL,7,Fon the Ayatollah's death, but shadow
OL,8,Fforeign secretary Dame Priti Patel
OL,9,Fsaid: "No-one should shed any tears
OL,10,Ffor the death of Khamenei."
OL,12,FSaturday's attack prompted retaliation
OL,13,Ffrom Iran, with strikes reported in
OL,14,Fseveral Gulf countries including the
OL,15,FUnited Arab Emirates, Qatar, Bahrain
OL,16,Fand Saudi Arabia.
OL,26,@qD@GOUrD@[O]
