OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772478696
OL,3,CIranian state TV says Supreme Leader
OL,4,CAyatollah Ali Khamenei has died
OL,6,FHundreds of thousands of British
OL,7,Fnationals are believed to be present
OL,8,Fin the Gulf, and those in Bahrain,
OL,9,FIsrael, Palestine, Qatar and the UAE
OL,10,Fhave been urged to register their
OL,11,Fpresence with the Foreign Office.
OL,13,FThe US and Israel described the
OL,14,Fattacks as a "pre-emptive" strike
OL,15,Fagainst a Tehran government intent on
OL,16,Fdeveloping nuclear weapons.
OL,26,@vD@NOUvD@ZO]
