PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1772478696
OL,3,CIranian state TV says Supreme Leader
OL,4,CAyatollah Ali Khamenei has died
OL,6,FIn a joint statement with the leaders
OL,7,Fof France and Germany, the Prime
OL,8,FMinister condemned Iran's retaliation
OL,9,Fand urged Tehran to "refrain from
OL,10,Findiscriminate military strikes" and
OL,11,F"seek a negotiated solution".
OL,13,FSpeaking from Downing Street, Sir Keir
OL,14,Fsaid the UK had not been involved in
OL,15,Fthe strikes, but had subsequently
OL,16,Fdeployed aircraft "as part of co-
OL,17,Fordinated regional defensive
OL,18,Foperations to protect our people, our
OL,19,Finterests and our allies".
